  "title": "Sales Solution Engineer (Business Development | Lead Generation | Valve & Actuators | 5 days)",
  "description": "<ul><li><strong>Well Establish Company</strong></li><li><strong>Basic $ 3,500- $5,000 + Allowances + AWS + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li><strong>Excellent Welfare and Benefits + Career progression</strong></li><li><strong>Working location: Tagore</strong></li><li><strong>Working hours: 8.30am to 5.30pm (Monday to Friday)</strong></li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Lead generation role and be responsible for conducting market research, developing solutions, prospecting, and expanding referral networks to seek out potential clients</strong></li><li>Coordinate Sales Efforts to Support Growth and Achieve Sales Targets</li><li>Maintain High Quality Customer Service by ensure responsive services with follow ups, build strong relationships clients</li><li>Respond to complaints from clients and give after-sales support on a timely basis</li><li>Provide technical support and advice for clients</li><li>Other ad hoc duties as assigned</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>At least 2 years of sales experience in the engineering or technical industry (e.g. Oil and Gas, Petrochemical, Pharmaceutical, Marine)</li><li><strong>Experience in Valve & Actuators will be a bonus</strong></li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via <strong>Apply Now</strong> button with the following information in the resume</p><ul><li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li><li>Current and Expected salary</li><li>Reason for leaving</li><li>Date of availability</li><li>Education background</li></ul><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p><p><br /></p><p>NG JYA YEE (R23119014)<br />EA Recruitment Pte Ltd<br />EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
